OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FLise McNally spoke to families who are
OL,8,Furging MPs to give more support to
OL,9,Fthose with Long Covid.
OL,11,FFamilies who have been struggling with
OL,12,Fthe impacts of Long Covid since the
OL,13,Fpandemic are urging the government to
OL,14,Fprovide more support.
OL,16,FAvalyn Godfrey was diagnosed with Long
OL,17,FCovid when she was 12, and now
OL,18,Fstruggles with exhaustion, brain fog,
OL,19,Fdizziness and joint pain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
