PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FDespite her symptoms seriously
OL,8,Faffecting her ability to stay in
OL,9,Fschool, her Long Covid was not deemed
OL,10,Fsuitable for an education health and
OL,11,Fcare plan (EHCP), leaving her family
OL,12,Fto self guide and self-fund so she can
OL,13,Ftake her GCSEs.
OL,15,FShe said: "I've been at two different
OL,16,Fhigh schools with chronic fatigue and
OL,17,Fchronic illness, and both of them
OL,18,Fweren't able to help me, they didn't
OL,19,Fknow what to do, how to support me.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"And I would have liked to get that
OL,8,Fsupport so I didn't have to leave.
OL,10,F"I would say it's really isolating.
OL,11,FAll my friends go to school together,
OL,12,Fand I would give anything to go to
OL,13,Fschool with them and do all the
OL,14,Flessons together now."
OL,16,FAvalyn was active in trapeze, sports
OL,17,Fand performing arts before she was
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with Long Covid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
