PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "I went from perfectly
OL,8,Fhealthy and alive, and then within a
OL,9,Fday my whole life was flipped around.
OL,10,FI was 12 and didn't know how to handle
OL,11,Fit.
OL,13,F"From then, it was a constant battle
OL,14,Fwith my own body, and that was really
OL,15,Fdifficult because it's something i'm
OL,16,Fnot going to win. Some days I'll wake
OL,17,Fup and don't want to wake up, I just
OL,18,Fwant to go back to sleep"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
