PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FAccording to charity Long Covid Kids
OL,8,F111,000 children were diagnosed with
OL,9,Fthe condition in 2024, with one in
OL,10,Ffive reporting serious limitations.
OL,12,FThe charity say no new data has been
OL,13,Fcollected since then, and no
OL,14,Fassessments have been made on the
OL,15,Fimpact it has on the young people
OL,16,Fbeing pushed out of education or
OL,17,Femployment.
OL,19,FParents say without proper data, the
OL,20,Feconomic impact of Long Covid is being
OL,21,Fsidelined.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
