OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FJane - whose daughter, Lydia, also
OL,8,Fsuffers with chronic illness due to
OL,9,FLong Covid - had to give up her 18-
OL,10,Fyear-career in science to care for her
OL,11,Ffull time.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's been devastating. It
OL,14,Fhas absolutely, overwhelmingly
OL,15,Fcapsized my life. As a mother you'd do
OL,16,Fanything to take your child's pain
OL,17,Faway.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"We could come up with a solution and
OL,8,Fmake the services fit for purpose.
OL,9,FListen to those people who are walking
OL,10,Fthe walk every single day and find out
OL,11,Fwhat is actually going on. Being heard
OL,12,Fis the biggest difficulty when people
OL,13,Fdon't open their minds.
OL,15,FJane says more research and
OL,16,Funderstanding is essential.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "The NHS struggles to
OL,8,Funderstand chronic illness and we
OL,9,Fhaven't found that there's any support
OL,10,Fat all and what support there is is
OL,11,Fminimal. We've been really left on our
OL,12,Fown."
OL,14,FJo Platt, Labour's Leigh and Atherton
OL,15,FMP - who was diagnosed with Long Covid
OL,16,Fin 2020 - says the first priority
OL,17,Fshould be more research into the
OL,18,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "There is lots that still
OL,8,Fneeds to happen, that recognition, the
OL,9,Fhealthcare profession within our
OL,10,Fhealthcare settings, within employment
OL,11,Fsettings, but also the research as
OL,12,Fwell.
OL,14,F"The fact that we now don't count Long
OL,15,FCovid is a problem because we don't
OL,16,Fknow what we're dealing with."
OL,18,FLong Covid Kids say more than 1,000
OL,19,Fpeople across the UK have been writing
OL,20,Fto their MP, calling for greater
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
