OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773493904
OL,3,C'It's capsized my life': Families
OL,4,Cstill affected by Long Covid want more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,Frecognition of Long Covid in children
OL,8,Fand young people, ahead of Long Covid
OL,9,FAwareness day on Sunday 15 March.
OL,11,FA government spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Frecognise the very real impact long
OL,13,FCovid continues to have on children
OL,14,Fand their families, and our thoughts
OL,15,Fare with all those affected.
OL,17,F"We have just published new guidance
OL,18,Ffor schools, designed in collaboration
OL,19,Fwith the Long Covid Kids charity, to
OL,20,Fhelp them support pupils.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
